These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, animation
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, chaman, bongani
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, rock
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, nigerian, british
House: wooden, modern, victorian
City: london, colone, venice
 1. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the modern house##3
 3. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is the fan of r&b##1
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the blend-smoker is the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person traveling to london is the nigerian##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is between the nigerian and the person traveling to venice##2
10. the person traveling to london is in an odd position##4
11. the blend-smoker is the british##1
12. the bongani-smoker is the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Movie-Genre          | comedy   | animation            | crime     |
| Cigar           | blend | bongani | chaman |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | rock               | r&b        |
| Nationality           | british        | indonesian         | nigerian   |
| House         | victorian     | modern      | wooden       |
| City     | venice        | colone              | london       |

