.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, chess, rock-climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, amber, emerald
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, dutch, egyptian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, trance
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, surfing, water-polo
3 different games are played: snooker, poker, whist
 1. the person who likes black is the egyptian##1
 2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who likes emerald is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person playing whist is between the person who likes black and the spanish##2
 6. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who likes amber and the person playing snooker##2
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 8. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of trance is the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Hobby      | writing | chess | rock-climbing        |
| Color          | amber   | emerald    | black        |
| Nationality   | spanish    | dutch | egyptian |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | ambient  | r&b         |
| Sport           | water-polo    | tennis | surfing       |
| Game     | poker   | whist    | snooker  |

