 7. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who likes azure##1
12. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

