 5. the person who likes blue is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 7. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of funk is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 9. the person who likes light-blue is between the owner of the horse and the victorian house##2
10. the person playing poker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |
