 5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 7. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the ranch-style house##1

