.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, august
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, airplane, train
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, amber, pink
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, indie, trance
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, tulip, poppy
3 different games are played: go, scrabble, snooker
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the fan of indie is between the person driving the airplane and the person who growspoppy##2
3. the person who growslily is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing go is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
5. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the fan of d&b is the person driving the train##1
8. the person playing go is between the person who likes black and the person who's birthday is in august##2
9. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Birthday      | august    | november           | april         |
| Transport         | train   | car             | airplane  |
| Color           | pink  | amber | black |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | indie              | trance      |
| Flower   | poppy | tulip             | lily     |
| Game         | scrabble   | go           | snooker      |

