.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: peach, potato, spinach
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, blue, white
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, fantasy, musical
3 different games are played: bridge, chess, billiard
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, september
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, 7up
 1. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 7. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the person who likes blue is the person eating potato##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3    |
| Food          | potato    | spinach  | peach   |
| Color   | blue      | apricot  | white  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | fantasy  | musical |
| Game           | chess     | bridge   | billiard   |
| Birthday         | april  | november | september |
| Beverage     | 7up   | almond-milk      | hot-chocolate  |

