.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, lily, iris
City: miami, marseilles, london
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, yellow, brown
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, japanese, thai
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, taxi, airplane
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is the person driving the airplane##1
 2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 3. the person who likes brown is the person who growsbellflower##1
 4. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
 6. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 8. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 9. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
10. the person drinking sprite is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |
| Flower          | lily     | iris   | bellflower     |
| City         | london | miami   | marseilles  |
| Beverage           | juice   | almond-milk | sprite   |
| Color   | azure    | yellow       | brown    |
| Nationality   | thai        | colombian    | japanese   |
| Transport         | taxi      | roller     | airplane |

 